query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS wateringLogs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  tentId INT NOT NULL,
  logDate DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  logTime VARCHAR(5) NOT NULL,
  volumeIn DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  volumeOut DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
  runoffPercent DECIMAL(5,2) NOT NULL,
  notes TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX idx_tent_date (tentId, logDate)
);
